9.1.4.3 `Local_Packages'
........................

Flag all local packages declared in package and generic package specs.
Local packages in bodies are not flagged.

This rule has no parameters.

Example
.......

    package Foo is
       package Inner is    --  FLAG
          I : Integer;
       end Inner;
    end Foo;


