flagged. The rule has an optional parameter for +R option:

`Except_USE_TYPE_Clauses'
     Do not flag local use type clauses.

Example
.......

    with Pack1;
    with Pack2;
    procedure Proc is
       use Pack1;               --  FLAG

       procedure Inner is
          use type Pack2.T;     --  FLAG (if Except_USE_TYPE_Clauses is not set)
